      <div class="story-content fade-up">
        <p>The name <strong>Techo</strong> carries a dual meaning that sits at the heart of everything we do. In the ancient Greek tradition, <em>Techne</em> referred not merely to technical skill, but to the mastery of craft — the ability to bring expertise and artistry together to create something that truly works. This is the standard we hold ourselves to in every project, every delivery, every product we manufacture.</p>
        <p>But "Techo" is also a roof. A shelter. A foundation above which everything else can be built with confidence. Techo Traders was founded with the ambition to be exactly that — the stable, trusted infrastructure beneath three growing industries, providing the resources, synergy, and strategic direction for each to reach its full potential.</p>
        <p>We began with a single observation: that the businesses of tomorrow would need to be simultaneously digital, physical, and connected. The companies that would win weren't the specialists — they were the ones who understood how all three worked together. So we built them ourselves.</p>
        <p>Today, Techo Traders is the parent organization of three distinctive subsidiaries, each a leader in its own domain, each strengthened by its siblings.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CORE VALUES -->
<section class="section section--off">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <div class="label" style="justify-content: center;">What We Stand For</div>
      <h2 class="section-heading">Core Values</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">01</div>
        <h4>SYNERGY</h4>
        <p>We believe the power of our ecosystem comes from how our companies interact — each one amplifying the capabilities of the others.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">02</div>
        <h4>INNOVATION</h4>
        <p>From the antennas we manufacture to the campaigns we run, we relentlessly pursue better solutions — never satisfied with the status quo.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">03</div>
        <h4>PRECISION</h4>
        <p>In manufacturing, in marketing, in logistics — precision is not optional. We sweat the details so our clients don't have to.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">04</div>
        <h4>STABILITY</h4>
        <p>We are the roof. Our partners, clients, and people rely on us to provide a consistent, dependable foundation for growth.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">05</div>
        <h4>INTEGRATION</h4>
        <p>Digital, physical, and hardware aren't separate worlds. We've built a company that proves they are strongest when unified.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card fade-up">
        <div class="value-card__number">06</div>
        <h4>INTEGRITY</h4>
        <p>Every relationship we build — with clients, partners, and our own team — is grounded in honesty, transparency, and trust.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VISION BAND -->
<section style="background: var(--blue); padding: 5rem 0;">
