      <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem); color: white; letter-spacing: 0.02em; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">TO BRIDGE THE GAP BETWEEN COMPLEX TECHNOLOGY AND EVERYDAY UTILITY</h2>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our vision is a Sri Lanka where every business — regardless of size or industry — has access to world-class digital tools, reliable logistics infrastructure, and cutting-edge hardware connectivity.</p>
